  "term": "thm:image-ops",
  "kind": "Theorem",
  "title": "Images and Set Operations",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $f : A \\to B$ and $S, T \\subseteq A$. Then\n- [label=(\\roman*)]\n- $f(S \\cup T) = f(S) \\cup f(T)$,\n- $f(S \\cap T) \\subseteq f(S) \\cap f(T)$,\n- $f(S \\setminus T) \\supseteq f(S) \\setminus f(T)$.\nEquality holds in (ii) and (iii) for all $S,T$ iff $f$ is injective.",
